    #if ((_Step)>0 andalso (_VarName_)<=(_End)) orelse ((_Step)<0 andalso (_VarName_)>=(_End))
      _Procedure( __FB_EVAL__(_VarName_) )
      const _VarName_##__Temp = ((_VarName_)+(_Step))
      #undef _VarName_
      const _VarName_ = _VarName_##__Temp
      #undef _VarName_##__Temp      
    #else
      #undef __mnext##_GB_
      #define __mnext##_GB_ rem        
    #endif       
    __mnext##_GB_( _VarName_ , (_Step) , (_End) , _Procedure )    
  #endmacro
#endmacro
#macro mfor( _Start , _End , _Step ,  _Procedure )    
  #if (_Step)=0
    #error " Step can't be 0"
  #else
    #if ((_Step)>0 andalso (_Start)<=(_End)) orelse ((_Step)<0 andalso (_Start)>=(_End))
      __GenMacro__mfor(1,2)
      __GenMacro__mfor(2,1)
      #undef _mforiterator_    
      const _mforiterator_ = ((_Start)+(_Step))    
      _Procedure( __FB_EVAL__(_Start) )    
      __mnext1( _mforiterator_ , (_Step) , (_End) , _Procedure )      
      #undef __mnext1
      #undef __mnext2
    #endif
  #endif
#endmacro
#define _to(_n) ,_n
#define _step(_n) ,_n
#define _do(_n) ,_n

  print __FB_QUOTE__( strings(i) )
#endmacro
mfor( 0 , 9 , 2 ,  DoIt )

  print "This will never print"
#endmacro
mfor( 9 _to(0) _step(1) _do(Irrelevant) )

  print chr(97+i);
#endmacro
mfor( 9 _to(0) _step(-1) _do(DoIt2) )
